description.en: Creators of Crypto Force digital comic series and future NFT Market for Comics, Illustrations and Concept Art Designs. $PINK will be the utility token of our evolving ecosystem. Token holders will receive many benefits, including but not limited to; exclusive NFT offers, future voting opportunities of the storyline in Crypto Force, and early access to the comic, if and when it moves to a subscription model. Our vision is a dynamic and popular comic series, with professional writers and illustrators, and special contributing artists from Marvel & DC comics. Additionally, we intend to be active in the artist community, by collaborating with a range of talented artists, hosting fan-art events, and inviting other comics to our future marketplace. Collectors will also be able to showcase their own NFTs in the collector's section.
